        { "@type": "Question", "name": "What are Copy.ai Workflows?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Workflows are multi-step AI pipelines that chain prompts, data lookups, and actions into automated jobs. Example: 'enrich a lead list, write personalised outreach for each, save to CRM'. The feature is the GTM pivot's most innovative product and competes with Clay and Apollo more than ChatGPT." }},
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Does Copy.ai write SEO articles?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Copy.ai generates drafts. It does not research keywords, analyse competitor SERPs, score against top-10 results, or auto-publish anywhere. The output reads well but is not SEO-optimised without additional tools." }},
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Is Copy.ai worth it in 2026?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "For GTM and sales ops teams running personalised outreach pipelines: yes — Workflows is a genuine differentiator. For solo copywriters: maybe — the free plan is generous, but ChatGPT Plus is more flexible. For SEO content marketing: no — pair with a real SEO tool or use a done-for-you service like theStacc ($99/mo)." }},
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Copy.ai vs Jasper — which is better?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Jasper has stronger marketing-team workflows, brand voice training, and integrations. Copy.ai has better Workflows (multi-step automations) and a more generous free plan. Pick Jasper for marketing-team content scale, Copy.ai for GTM automation." }},
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Does Copy.ai have a free plan?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes — 2,000 words per month free, with most features unlocked for one user. It is one of the most generous free tiers in the AI writing category. Hits the cap fast for long-form work but is genuinely useful for short-form." }},
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "What are the best Copy.ai alternatives?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Jasper ($49/mo) for marketing teams. Writesonic ($49/mo) for 80+ templates. ChatGPT Plus ($20/mo) for raw flexibility. Clay ($149/mo) for stronger GTM workflows. For done-for-you SEO content with publishing, theStacc ($99/mo) handles 30 articles per month directly to your CMS." }}
      ]
    }
  ]
};
