              <tr><td>Short-form copywriting</td><td class="cell-yes">Excellent for marketing copy</td><td>SEO-focused, fewer templates</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Workflows (GTM automation)</td><td class="cell-yes">Genuinely innovative</td><td class="cell-no">Not the job</td></tr>
              <tr><td>SEO articles written for you</td><td>Generates drafts, no SEO optimisation</td><td class="cell-yes">30 SEO-optimised articles / month</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Auto-publishes to your CMS</td><td class="cell-no">Copy / paste only</td><td class="cell-yes">WordPress · Webflow · Ghost</td></tr>
