        <p>The free plan covers 2,000 words/month for one user with most features unlocked — genuinely generous. Pro at $49/mo unlocks unlimited Chat and Workflows. Advanced is where teams get serious Workflow runs and seat allowances. Annual billing saves 25%.</p>

