        <h2 id="verdict">Is Copy.ai worth it in 2026? Final verdict</h2>
        <p><strong>For sales and RevOps teams: yes, on Advanced.</strong> Workflows is genuinely innovative and a real differentiator vs Jasper and Writesonic. If your job is personalised outreach at scale, $249/mo is fair value.</p>

        <p><strong>For solo marketers: yes, on Free or Pro.</strong> The free plan covers most short-form needs. Pro at $49/mo unlocks unlimited Chat and Workflows for one user.</p>

